@
State of ospf6d

It does not work yet
work in (slow) progress

Hello protocol, neighbor and interface state machine work

LSDB and flooding are usable but not fully correct

interpretation of the various LSA and the SPF algorithm are not yet done
kroute code can be used for some stuff
redistribution and all other fancy options are missing

@
